indings, we extend an established dynamical nuclear\npolarization model to take into account optically detuned quantum dots for\nwhich nuclear spins activate additional electron spin precession modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2018 16:04:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Aug 2018 11:15:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-15"}
