ations\nalone. A simple model of an isolated, isothermal cylinder may not provide a\ngood approach for fragmentation analysis, independently of the dominant driving\nsource of the parental cloud.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2018 16:24:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-07"}
