, and Horologium~II; however, due to the small\nnumber of members in each satellite, spectroscopic follow-up observations are\nnecessary to determine the systemic proper motion in these satellites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2018 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Feb 2019 21:26:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-24"}
